{"tid":732502,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[節拍遊戲]一齊投入Lanota嘅世界啦！","createTime":"2018-07-07T03:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T04:48:24.000Z","uid":64884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"15e69c98a8292854c9b94fafea50e39c09cde3ab","tid":732502,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36235935_2244599682223180_1797094361951895552_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=2d2f90d9bfc9238eef051fb05b3f5ed9&amp;oe=5BA73879\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36235935_2244599682223180_1797094361951895552_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D2d2f90d9bfc9238eef051fb05b3f5ed9%26oe%3D5BA73879&h=4ef183fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36330918_2246148818734933_877015038894800896_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=a9e941ca9d7c066eb730012166dfeaa7&amp;oe=5BD90EE7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36330918_2246148818734933_877015038894800896_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Da9e941ca9d7c066eb730012166dfeaa7%26oe%3D5BD90EE7&h=4c4efb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQ: 咩係Lanota?<br />\nA: Lanota係由Noxy Games推出嘅繪本風RPG節拍game，可謂繼Rayark出嘅節拍遊戲後嘅另一台產佳作！<br />\n<br />\nQ: 背景故事大約講咩?<br />\nA: 在250年前，世界因為「靜默化」的災難而使得大部分的場所皆失去了聲音與色彩。只有使用前人創造出的一種能源濃縮體─「音礦」，才能讓這些場所恢復原狀。只不過以現在的技術，已經無法再次製造出這個人工物質。為了要一=邊確保世界的正常運作並將受到災害影響的地方恢復原狀，唯一手段便是再利用過去的人們遺留下的音礦。<br />\n<br />\n本遊戲將由玩家扮演主角菲希卡與里莫，兩人帶著所擁有的「音礦調律裝置」，將各個場所不可利用的「無序」音礦，「調律」至可正常運作的「有序」狀態，進而恢復世界的聲音與色彩。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解玩Lanota?<br />\nA: Lanota嘅原型係嚟自機舖嘅Maimai，但佢打破咗physical嘅限制，令圓盤可以旋轉、平移、瞬移等，再搭配創新嘅譜面，拉、打、撳同上下移，玩法可以話係千變萬化。獨特嘅世界觀、繪本風加上BGM嘅烘托，帶出fantasy、hopeless但有一絲曙光嘅氣氛，令玩家可以全程投入Lanota嘅世界。搭配不同風格但同樣動人嘅歌曲， 集Cytus嘅創新同Deemo嘅故事性一身！每個chapter都有精心設計嘅魔王曲配以精緻嘅動畫，挑戰你感官嘅極限！價錢十分實惠只需$15，當然入面有side story買。如果玩悶咗story mode，佢仲有啲擴充包係即打嘅譜面，不過得一個chapter，其他就要買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係介紹影片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrwivWBIQU7cqA3zyASWKeQ/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCrwivWBIQU7cqA3zyASWKeQ%2Fvideos&d=bfsb2Z%2BflDqDUoBqCQS%2FZkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ac9a9cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrwivWBIQU7cqA3zyASWKeQ/videos</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook Page:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lanota/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flanota%2F&d=bfsb2Z%2BflDqDUoBqCQS%2FZkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=f666834d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lanota/</a>"},{"pid":"e61bea5d7c6c3482104531c66740526727c60fe7","tid":732502,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e69c98a8292854c9b94fafea50e39c09cde3ab","tid":732502,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36235935_2244599682223180_1797094361951895552_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=2d2f90d9bfc9238eef051fb05b3f5ed9&amp;oe=5BA73879\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36235935_2244599682223180_1797094361951895552_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D2d2f90d9bfc9238eef051fb05b3f5ed9%26oe%3D5BA73879&h=4ef183fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36330918_2246148818734933_877015038894800896_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=a9e941ca9d7c066eb730012166dfeaa7&amp;oe=5BD90EE7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36330918_2246148818734933_877015038894800896_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Da9e941ca9d7c066eb730012166dfeaa7%26oe%3D5BD90EE7&h=4c4efb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQ: 咩係Lanota?<br />\nA: Lanota係由Noxy Games推出嘅繪本風RPG節拍game，可謂繼Rayark出嘅節拍遊戲後嘅另一台產佳作！<br />\n<br />\nQ: 背景故事